Author: Tiny_Buttercups98
Text: Oof been there but it was setting my WhatsApp profile photo the same as my Instagram. Not as bad but I got a text from my sister and a few friends being like 'Is ThAt YoU?'  One of the most mortifying things I've done, apart from drunkenly confessing my eating issues with people from work, needless to say I immediately changed my photo and set my insta to private
